                     String request,

        Calls a REST service that posts an XML object representation, and returns a location header containing the new object's URL. Calls RestTemplate method of the same name
        Parameters:
        url - the URL of the REST service.
        request - the XML representation of the object being posted
        args - arguments to be used to fill in any URL placeholders
        Returns:
        the URL at which the POSTed object can be found
